# T1047 - Windows Management Instrumentation Detection
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1047 - Windows Management Instrumentation
# Description: Detect suspicious WMI usage for lateral movement, persistence, and execution

# First, let's analyze what WMI events we have from the simulation
index=win earliest=-24h
| search (EventCode=1 OR EventCode=4688)
| search (wmi* OR winmgmt OR scrcons OR wmiprvse OR wmic OR "Windows Management Instrumentation")
| head 50
| table _time, EventCode, _raw

CREDENTIAL DUMPING: https://github.com/splunk/security_content/blob/develop/detections/endpoint/windows_possible_credential_dumping.yml